OL,3,CPremier League calls meeting as City
OL,4,Cclaim victory after landmark ruling
OL,6,FWhile the Premier League and
OL,7,FManchester City are both claiming
OL,8,Fvictory in a landmark legal judgement
OL,9,Freleased today, it is likely the
OL,10,Fcurrent champions will be sleeping
OL,11,Fmore easily tonight.
OL,13,FAlso, on a seismic day, some of City's
OL,14,Ftitle rivals will be deeply concerned
OL,15,Fabout the ramifications of the case,
OL,16,Fafter a panel found that sections of
OL,17,Fthe League's Associated Party
OL,18,FTransaction (APT) rules were unlawful.
