OL,3,CPremier League calls meeting as City
OL,4,Cclaim victory after landmark ruling
OL,6,FThose ramifications will be discussed
OL,7,Fat an emergency meeting of all 20
OL,8,FPremier League clubs next week. The
OL,9,Fhearing's conclusions have threatened
OL,10,Fto spark a financial civil war within
OL,11,FEnglish football.
OL,13,FThe Premier League's APT rules are
OL,14,Fdesigned to ensure that any
OL,15,Fsponsorship deal a club does with a
OL,16,Fcompany linked to its owners is of
OL,17,F'Fair Market Value' (FMV).
