OL,3,CPremier League calls meeting as City
OL,4,Cclaim victory after landmark ruling
OL,6,FIn a judgement that will send shivers
OL,7,Fthrough the league, the tribunal found
OL,8,Fthat the current APT rules are
OL,9,Funlawful under the Competition Act. It
OL,10,Fbased that decision on the grounds
OL,11,Fthat the rules do not incorporate
OL,12,Fshareholder loans.
OL,14,FThese are loans an owner or
OL,15,Fshareholder may make to a club but
OL,16,Fbecause of their close relationship
OL,17,Fwill charge little or no interest.
OL,19,FManchester City's lawyers argued
OL,20,Fsuccessfully that these loans should
OL,21,Fbe part of the APT system.
