OL,3,CPremier League calls meeting as City
OL,4,Cclaim victory after landmark ruling
OL,6,FIt's currently estimated that
OL,7,Fcombined, Premier League clubs enjoy
OL,8,F#1.5 billion of these favourable loans
OL,9,Fwhich currently sit outside the Profit
OL,10,Fand Sustainability Rules (PSR).
OL,12,FThese are the regulations that Everton
OL,13,Fand Nottingham Forest fell foul of and
OL,14,Fled them to being docked points.
OL,16,FIt's thought that if all clubs had to
OL,17,Fapply the generally accepted level of
OL,18,Finterest payments, several of them
OL,19,Fwould struggle to meet PSR
OL,20,Frequirements.
