OL,3,CPremier League calls meeting as City
OL,4,Cclaim victory after landmark ruling
OL,6,FThe tribunal also ruled that the APT
OL,7,Frules were unlawful because they were
OL,8,F"procedurally unfair."
OL,10,FSpecifically, the panel found in
OL,11,Ffavour of Manchester City because the
OL,12,Fclub was not allowed to make
OL,13,Frepresentations about the data the
OL,14,FPremier League used to assess FMV.
OL,16,FThis applied to two large sponsorship
OL,17,Fdeals, from associated parties, that
OL,18,FCity were barred from accepting.
