OL,3,CPremier League calls meeting as City
OL,4,Cclaim victory after landmark ruling
OL,6,FThe tribunal signalled that it would
OL,7,Fpotentially consider losses incurred
OL,8,Fby City in due course.
OL,10,FThe dominant force in English football
OL,11,Fsaid today the ruling showed the
OL,12,FLeague had "abused its dominant
OL,13,Fposition".
OL,15,FWhile all the above feels like a dark
OL,16,Fday for the Premier League and its
OL,17,Fleadership, they are also claiming a
OL,18,F'win.'
