OL,3,CPremier League calls meeting as City
OL,4,Cclaim victory after landmark ruling
OL,6,FMainly it seems because the panel
OL,7,Fupheld the need for the APT system,
OL,8,Fand rejected the majority of
OL,9,FManchester City's challenges.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the Premier League
OL,12,Fsaid it welcomed the tribunal's
OL,13,Ffindings "which endorsed the overall
OL,14,Fobjectives, framework and decision-
OL,15,Fmaking of the APT system."
OL,17,FThe panel's exact wording was "The APT
OL,18,FRules are designed precisely to ensure
OL,19,Fthat competition is not distorted
OL,20,Fbetween clubs that use Associated
OL,21,FParties and those that do not".
