OL,3,CPremier League calls meeting as City
OL,4,Cclaim victory after landmark ruling
OL,6,FA victory of sorts, however, the
OL,7,FPremier League did accept the tribunal
OL,8,Fidentified a "small number of discrete
OL,9,Felements" that didn't comply with
OL,10,Fcompetition law.
OL,12,F"These elements" the statement went on
OL,13,F"can be quickly and effectively
OL,14,Fremedied by the League and clubs."
OL,16,FElements that will be front and centre
OL,17,Fof what is likely to be a tense
OL,18,Fmeeting of all clubs next week.
